to supply you with more details

00:30:32.682 --> 00:30:36.477 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
about how you can increase
your knowledge of the Bible

00:30:36.477 --> 00:30:38.521 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and its Author, Jehovah God.

00:30:41.608 --> 00:30:46.446 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What an encouraging session
